    "description": "<strong>欢迎来到罗马征服世界的战乱时代。 </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/a7cbd32ea83ee4d57e8c8540bdc33c0d.poster.avif?t=1715600730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/a7cbd32ea83ee4d57e8c8540bdc33c0d.webm?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/a7cbd32ea83ee4d57e8c8540bdc33c0d.mp4?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《军团战魂：罗马》是一款以罗马历史为背景的动作冒险RPG，游戏操作着重于多方向战斗系统。玩家扮演忠心的罗马军团指挥官，为了帝国的荣耀可以毫不留情地消灭蛮族部落。为了罗马，为了世界和平，为了胜利，为了回到家人的怀抱，你将大开杀戒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>沙场兄弟：</strong>在大大小小的战斗中善用小队战术来击败敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>一夫当关：</strong>利用特殊战斗机制斩断敌人手脚、首级。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>技能强化：</strong>随着在战场上升级，你将会解锁更多不同的技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>战场荣耀：</strong>逼真的画面带领你进入最真实的战场实况。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>历史背景：</strong>罗马不是只有战场厮杀，在游戏中了解罗马历史与故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/8b19adecd7acadfffd89cb27c1a269f3.webp?t=1715600730\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <strong>家人通信：</strong>寄送家书给等你回去的家人，让他们了解战争的意义，并阅读他们回信。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1715600730\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><strong>为罗马带来和平与荣耀，无论代价。</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/6c0bc3dce9a128927c111d96ac53503a.poster.avif?t=1715600730\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/6c0bc3dce9a128927c111d96ac53503a.webm?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/6c0bc3dce9a128927c111d96ac53503a.mp4?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的任务是为世界带来和平与荣耀，将罗马法律与文化传播到世界的尽头。战争中没有所谓的残暴，你可以不择手段，因为这是战争。<br><br><u><strong>准备战斗</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/0d99aef2f09a5139baeb09500fbc95e4.poster.avif?t=1715600730\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/0d99aef2f09a5139baeb09500fbc95e4.webm?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/0d99aef2f09a5139baeb09500fbc95e4.mp4?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>拿起你的剑，穿上你的盔甲，让不愿跪倒在罗马面前的人染红你的武器。<br><br><u><strong>维持军队纪律</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/113dcf83502bed86ce18ea393686f303.poster.avif?t=1715600730\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/113dcf83502bed86ce18ea393686f303.webm?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120790/extras/113dcf83502bed86ce18ea393686f303.mp4?t=1715600730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>蛮族部落大军集结！维持军队纪律和士气是获得胜利的要素。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入我们的官方 Discord 频道与我们分享你的意见。</h2><br><br>",
